\n用完個framework都仲係好raw，咩春都要自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上個library有啲function會有bug，仲要幫佢fix埋bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />error throw又做得差，永遠console見到紅字都係JavaScript runtime本身throw出嚟果嘅error，變左要自己debug個library source code睇下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，community又細，中途好後悔點解唔用unreal/unity<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾第二個project有用過unreal立即覺得好輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都係unity最易用，基本上咩嘢都有哂"},{"pid":"6c2668d6b20679331ba331b2cb3471d385bd6a57","tid":2336237,"uid":37475,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:09:19.000Z","msg":"講真香港唔係公司裡面做<br />\n要搵隻做到完既遊戲少之又少<br />\n原因太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間係其中一個重要原因"},{"pid":"d9ee0e99e23285b2992431cf0766900890138423","tid":2336237,"uid":249170,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9dffb51bf3d800da7b710e8cac013c3a4f344391","tid":2336237,"uid":72631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"我試過用Phaser js寫足一年html5 canvas game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用完個framework都仲係好raw，咩春都要自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上個library有啲function會有bug，仲要幫佢fix埋bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />error throw又做得差，永遠console見到紅字都係JavaScript runtime本身throw出嚟果嘅error，變左要自己debug個library source code睇下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，community又細，中途好後悔點解唔用unreal/unity<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾第二個project有用過unreal立即覺得好輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都係unity最易用，基本上咩嘢都有哂"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"終於見到知音，忍唔住入黎回<br />\nPhaser我都用過一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(果陣公司接左Project要做，但發覺中伏入坑，最後用左GameMaker 趕工，公司gamemaker 有哂成set license)<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得Phaser 2 好用亦都完善過 Phaser 3，可惜兩者唔兼容，但外國人肯定叫你用Phaser 3，而且Phaser 4都就黎出 ，好快又要學過新<br />\n<br />\n用Phaser寫Game真係行好撚多冤枉路<br />\n用得Phaser真係預左咩春都要自己寫，如果Export到Mobile, 要用較落後既Phonegap或Cordova，仲要唔同Mobile Device performance 都唔同,有d機 fps好低30以下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果果隻game有物理效果(例如寫超音鼠，個player可企係斜向既平台)，就要學撚埋超難學既Matterjs,(phaser 2既p2js可能易學d，但仆街作者rich係都要係phaser3用matterjs,屌佢老母西)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要寫HTML5 Game, 一係用Construct 3，一係用GameMaker 2<br />\n用Phaser 揼code揼撚死你<br />\n<br />\n同埋寫網頁HTML5 game有一樣唔好既地方，就係好易比人用Chrome 拎哂你d遊戲圖同音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以寫game，你d圖係畫得好辛苦或者好貴買返黎，就盡量避免寫網頁HTML5 遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果學大路game engine建議直接用unity,unreal,godot, 一定冇行錯冤枉路"},{"pid":"d3595858e68a23d9b19531b636b300224f6bcbfa","tid":2336237,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"84023a8457c22eb45962f0bb59e799a2724f9737","tid":2336237,"uid":37475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:38:19.000Z","msg":"有無整到半路既圖睇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb869b090d586de154ea7b09ef497b368d9d80aa","tid":2336237,"uid":249170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35d8d0880bca85aaf2ca0b7a656a12e04978a5a4","tid":2336237,"uid":80902,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"唔少人用RPG maker整Game放上steam賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好玩既話我覺得無問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />