sets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以寫game，你d圖係畫得好辛苦或者好貴買返黎，就盡量避免寫網頁HTML5 遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果學大路game engine建議直接用unity,unreal,godot, 一定冇行錯冤枉路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"睇你篇嘢好似見到自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢啲function仲要一啲都唔friendly，下上都要自己wrap完先好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔明user諗到既嘢點解library developer諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf15943838f8bcfed5f2b8c4b8044b157a399974","tid":2336237,"uid":72631,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9dffb51bf3d800da7b710e8cac013c3a4f344391","tid":2336237,"uid":72631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:02:38.000Z","msg":"我試過用Phaser js寫足一年html5 canvas game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用完個framework都仲係好raw，咩春都要自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上個library有啲function會有bug，仲要幫佢fix埋bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />error throw又做得差，永遠console見到紅字都係JavaScript runtime本身throw出嚟果嘅error，變左要自己debug個library source code睇下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，community又細，中途好後悔點解唔用unreal/unity<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾第二個project有用過unreal立即覺得好輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過都係unity最易用，基本上咩嘢都有哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"例如寫個對話dialogue，先要有個背景色，之後係上面加字，加完字之後你發現句中文句子太長會出界，之後要自己搵alogrithm唔夠位就break下一行。做完basic ui之後要自己寫一個flow engine比佢禁返上一頁對話，同埋下一頁對話，每轉一頁就要trigger某啲event轉埋成個canvas既公仔/背景etc。，最後發現句句子再長係會穿底，今次又要detect到無位就分多個對話dialogue係下一頁。好啦諗住終於完，想highlights句子中間既重點先發現又要自己搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7587e1a260b1baa9bc3698a56c51bbbe5835af39","tid":2336237,"uid":37475,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PeTuAs9HHkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPeTuAs9HHkc&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpF6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=c274328f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PeTuAs9HHkc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nZdZJt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nZdZJt.jpg&h=10c2b58a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同個fd 合作整到一半（？）"},{"pid":"60bb06c4e030dd8440e044bbf8720d1f72932f3d","tid":2336237,"uid":37475,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/1337710/X/?l=tchinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1337710%2FX%2F%3Fl%3Dtchinese&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpF6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=771e831f\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/1337710/X/?l=tchinese</a><br />\n<br />\n未完成試玩"},{"pid":"39cf9eb6fcf05596672ce02438be8e1ac1422fa0","tid":2336237,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"Unity 好似唔錯"},{"pid":"3899b6f9db847b245ec1da4c80a7716712370376","tid":2336237,"uid":118087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7587e1a260b1baa9bc3698a56c51bbbe5835af39","tid":2336237,"uid":37475,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PeTuAs9HHkc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPeTuAs9HHkc&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpF6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=c274328f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PeTuAs9HHkc</a><br />\n<img sr